ZH: 凡事要有耐心，才能取得成功。
EN: Patience is necessary for success in everything.

ZH: 凡事都要保持积极的心态。
EN: It is important to maintain a positive attitude in everything.

ZH: 凡事有计划地去做，才会更顺利。
EN: Everything goes smoother when done with a plan.

ZH: 凡事先做好准备，就可以避免很多麻烦。
EN: Being prepared beforehand can help avoid many troubles.

ZH: 凡事要量力而为，不可过度劳累。
EN: Do everything within your abilities, do not overexert yourself.

ZH: 凡事都需要时间去磨练和成长。
EN: Everything requires time for practice and growth.

ZH: 凡事都要讲求效率，避免浪费时间。
EN: Efficiency should be prioritized in everything to avoid wasting time.

ZH: 凡事要有始有终，不可半途而废。
EN: Complete everything you start, do not give up halfway.

ZH: 凡事要相信自己的能力，不要自我怀疑。
EN: Believe in your own abilities in everything, do not doubt yourself.

ZH: 凡事要控制好情绪，不要因小事发脾气。
EN: Keep emotions in check in everything, do not lose your temper over trivial matters.

ZH: 凡事要学会宽容，不要过于苛求他人。
EN: Learn to be tolerant in everything, do not demand too much from others.

ZH: 凡事要追求进步，不要满足于现状。
EN: Strive for progress in everything, do not settle for the status quo.

ZH: 凡事都要注重细节，做到尽善尽美。
EN: Pay attention to details in everything, strive for perfection.

ZH: 凡事要勇于尝试，不可畏惧失败。
EN: Be brave enough to try everything, do not fear failure.

ZH: 凡事要认真核实事实，不要随意妄下结论。
EN: Verify facts diligently in everything, do not draw conclusions recklessly.

ZH: 凡事都要持之以恒，不要半途而废。
EN: Persevere in everything, do not give up halfway.

ZH: 凡事要多思考，不要盲目行动。
EN: Think more in everything, do not act blindly.

ZH: 凡事要坚持原则，不可动摇。
EN: Stick to principles in everything, do not waver.

ZH: 凡事要关心他人，不要只顾自己。
EN: Show concern for others in everything, do not only think of yourself.

ZH: 凡事都要理性对待，不要过于情绪化。
EN: Approach everything rationally, do not be overly emotional.
